{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "25", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "20", "M": "27", "S": "06"}}, "news": [{"title": "Women owners in Pune to get 50% property tax discount", "para": "Pune Municipal Corporation (PMC) has disappointed small property owners by not announcing a blanket tax waiver as promised. Instead, only women property owners will receive a 50% tax discount, a move civic activists have criticized as a betrayal of electoral promises. The civic body aims to generate revenue through an amnesty scheme for unauthorized constructions and by recovering outstanding dues.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/pune-municipal-corporation-offers-50-property-tax-discount-for-women-property-owners/129790010?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-84008/129790010.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Visakhapatnam civic body's property tax collections cross \u20b9510 crore", "para": "Greater Visakhapatnam Municipal Corporation has achieved a record \u20b9510 crore in property tax collections for the 2025-26 fiscal year, surpassing last year's \u20b9500 crore. Officials anticipate reaching \u20b9600 crore by March 31, boosted by a 50% state government interest waiver on pending dues and focused efforts on vacant land tax and arrears.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/visakhapatnam-municipal-corporation-hits-record-property-tax-collection-of-510-crore/129789982?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-63306/129789982.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Illegal sand mining flourishes along Saberi river bed in Koraput", "para": "Large-scale illegal sand mining is rampant along the Saberi riverbed in Koraput district, with tipper trucks openly transporting sand i